  }}</ref><ref>Hill, I. D., Horvath, K., and Fasano, A., ''Epidemiology of celiac disease.'' 1: Am J Gastroenterol. 1995 Jan;90(1):163-4</ref>具有非洲人，日本人和中国人的血统的人中很少发现患有乳糜泻的。<ref>{{Cite journal |author=Houlston RS, Ford D |year=1996 |title=Genetics of coeliac disease |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_qjm_1996-10_89_10/page/737 |journal=QJM |volume=89 |issue=10 |pages=737–43 |pmid=8944229 |doi=10.1093/qjmed/89.10.737}}</ref>乳糜泻在女性中比在男性中更流行。<ref>{{Cite journal |last1=Hischenhuber |first1=C |last2=Crevel |first2=R |last3=Jarry |first3=B |first4=M |last4=Mäki |first5=D A |last5=Moneret-Vautrin |first6=A |last6=Romano |first7=R |last7=Troncone |first8=R |last8=Ward |title=Review article: safe amounts of gluten for patients with wheat allergy or coeliac disease |journal=Aliment. Pharmacol. Ther. |volume=23 |issue=5 |pages=559–75 |pmid=16480395 |doi=10.1111/j.1365-2036.2006.02768.x |url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1365-2036.2006.02768.x/full |date=March 2006 |access-date=2013-10-02 |archive-date=2013-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012060604/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1365-2036.2006.02768.x/full |dead-url=no }}</ref>

乳糜泻是[[免疫系统|免疫系统]]对{{Link-en|麸朊|gliadin}}产生不良反应所造成的疾病。麸朊是一种在小麦（和{{Link-en|小麦族|Triticeae}}中其它类似的谷物，比如[[大麦|大麦]]和[[黑麦|黑麦]]）中发现的[[麸质|麸质]]蛋白质。对待乳糜泻仅有的有效方法就是终生实行[[无麸质饮食|无麸质饮食]]。

